OL,3,CArtemis II astronauts rocket towards
OL,4,Cthe moon after leaving Earth's orbit
OL,6,FThe Orion capsule has bolted out of
OL,7,Forbit around Earth and chased after
OL,8,Fthe moon nearly 250,000 miles away.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FIt is the first engine firing for a
OL,16,Fmoon crew since Apollo 17 set out on
OL,17,Fthat era's final moonshot in 1972.
