OL,3,CArtemis II astronauts rocket towards
OL,4,Cthe moon after leaving Earth's orbit
OL,6,FNASA had the Artemis II crew stick
OL,7,Fclose to home for a day to test their
OL,8,Fcapsule's life-support systems before
OL,9,Fclearing them for lunar departure.
OL,11,F"Humanity has once again shown what we
OL,12,Fare capable of, and it's your hopes
OL,13,Ffor the future that carry us now on
OL,14,Fthis journey around the moon,"
OL,15,FCanadian Space Agency astronaut Jeremy
OL,16,FHansen said in the crew's first words
OL,17,Fsince they set course.
