OL,3,CArtemis II astronauts rocket towards
OL,4,Cthe moon after leaving Earth's orbit
OL,6,F"The first thing I would say is, trust
OL,7,Fus, you look amazing. You look
OL,8,Fbeautiful," NASA astronaut Victor
OL,9,FGlover said. "And from up here, you
OL,10,Falso look like one thing. Homo sapiens
OL,11,Fis all of us, no matter where you're
OL,12,Ffrom or what you look like. We're all
OL,13,Fone people."
OL,15,FThe Artemis II mission will be a 10-
OL,16,Fday trip around the moon and back,
OL,17,Fwithout landing on the moon's surface.
